column2: "Wow, thanks! It's like a dream all of the things you've collected for me!"
"Aha! It's still early for Christmas, but for me and the children, you're like Santa!"
"The venue is completely decorated! The dishes are all prepared! The presents are all here, and everyone is healthy!"
"Now I've just got to do what I can! Alright, awesome!"
"I'm absolutely going to show you the best Christmas party ever! Honestly, thanks so much!"
